Takotaa Hayɩ Kiŋ kɛna [[Etaazuunii|Etaazunii]] ɛjaɖɛ taa tɛtʊ cikpetʊ natʊyʊ. Nɛ Etazuunii ɛjaɖɛ ɖɩnɛ ɖɩ-taa lɛ ajɛya cikpena naayɛ nɩɩnɩwa kpɛndɩna nɛ aɖʊ nɔɔ nɛ awɛɛ ɛjaɖɛ kʊɖʊmɖɩyɛ taa kpaɩ. Etaazunii tɔbʊʊ nɛ kabɩyɛ taa se ajɛya kɩkpɛndʊʊ. Takota taa tɛtʊ sɔsɔtʊ payaɣ se Bismark nɛ ndʊ tɩ-taa ɛyaa kɩla ɖɔʊ yɔ ndʊ lɛ Fargo.

Tɛtʊ ndʊ tɩcɔ ɛjaɖɛ cikpeɖe ɖɩnɛ nɛ tɩta yɔ ndʊ yɔ: Wɩsɩ ɖɩlɩyɛ taa lɛ [[Minesootaa]], wɩsɩ ɖɩɖʊyɛ taa kiŋ lɛ [[Mɔntanaa|Montanaa]] hadɛ kiŋ lɛ [[Takota nɛ hadɛ kiŋ|Takota nɛ hadɛ kɩŋ]] piyele nɛ hayʊ kiŋ lɛ [[Kanadaa]] ageeta naayɛ ñɛwɛna.
